name: Quinton
content:
Quinton was a Human male smuggler who lived during the Galactic Civil War. He was a smuggler and partner to Harding. They had an operation on the forest moon of Endor.
Quinton was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Quinton was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
